title: d5-4 mid lanner looking for a ranked 5s/OOL team

body:
Hey all,
looking for a ranked 5s/OOL team to play on.

replies.body: Requirements are: Must be able to trust our shot caller, Discord, Scrims weekly, OOL every 2nd weekend accept criticism, and Ranked 5s regulary :)
We have a pretty Stacked Plat + team 4 diamonds and 4/5 plats you keen?
